nodes.title: NAG notes
widgets_values:
Using NAG like Perturbed Attention to increase coherence and details.

Correction of overcooked image / color levels in post-processing pass.

## masslevel NAG values

### optimized

- nag_scale: 50
- nag_alpha: 0.27
- nag_tau: 3

### high

- nag_scale: 80
- nag_alpha: 0.3
- nag_tau: 4

## default values

- nag_scale: 11
- nag_alpha: 0.25
- nag_tau: 2.500

## nag_scale

The scale for attention feature extrapolation. Higher values result in stronger negative guidance.

## nag_alpha

Blending factor between original and extrapolated attention. Higher values result in stronger negative guidance.

## nag_tau

The normalisation threshold. Higher values result in stronger negative guidance.
